Wu S, Wang D, Liu J, Feng Y, Weng J, Li Y, Gao X, Liu J, Wang W: The dynamic multisite interactions between two intrinsically disordered proteins. Angew Chem Int Ed Engl 2017, 56:7515-7519 The authors combined NMR, single-molecule FRET, and MD simulations to show that two IDPs form a complex with pronounced structural disorder mediated by multiple binding sites, primarily hydrophobic and residue-specific.
