49. 
Ruff KM, Pappu RV, Holehouse AS: Conformational preferences and phase behavior of intrinsically disordered low complexity sequences: insights from multiscale simulations. Curr Opin Struct Biol 2019, 56:1-10
Excellent review summarizing the state-of-the-art in simulations of disordered proteins and regions across a wide range of scale and resolution, with a particular focus on different levels of coarse-graining.
